'''Aɛmar n At Ḥemmuda''', d yiwen n urgaz, n umeɣras n tlelli, n timunent n tmurt n Lzzayer.

Illul deg usegwas n [[1923]] deg tama n [[Tasaft Ugemmun]]. Yettwanɣa deg usegwas n [[1956]] axaṭer d yiwen n umeɣras n Tizzayrit.

Deg segwasen n 40, yetteki deg yiwet n tarbaɛt yekkaten ɣef Lzzayer Tazzayrit, anda ilaq ad yilli wemkan i Tmaziɣt (ladɣa Taqabylit).



== Tameddurt-is == 

Aɛmar At Ḥemmuda aẓar-is n taddart n Tasaft Ugemmun deg tama n [[Ibudraren]], deg tlemmast n wedrar n [[Ǧerger]]. Yettili-yas i "colonel" Aɛmiruc ([[Amiruc n At Ḥemmuda]]). 

Aɛmar At Ḥemmuda yella yeqqar deg uɣerbaz "Ecole Normale" di Buzriɛa deg Lzzayer. Yeɣra daɣen deg  tama n Bufarik, Tamelyant akwd Benɛknun.  

Di Benɛkun yetteki deg tarbaɛt umi qqaren "Tarbaɛt n inelmaden n Tesdawit n Benɛkun" ar tama n [[Ḥusin At Ḥmed]], [[Saɛid Cciban]], [[Ɛumar Usediq]], [[Muḥend  At Ɛemran]], [[Benay Waɛli]].

Asmi yexsar akayad-ines n le bac, yekkcem dɣa ar ukabar n PPA anda yennuɣ ɣef Lzzayer Tazzayrit si tazwara n usegwas n 1942. 

Aɛmar At Ḥemmuda d yiwen n umeɣnas n tarbaɛt n "l'OS", tarbaɛt n umenuɣ tufirt, yettusema ɣef uqarruy n tarbaɛt-aggi deg tama n tmurt n Yeqbayliyen (kabylie). 

Deg usegwas n 1948, Aɛmar At Ḥemmuda yettusema am umerccaḥ (candidat) deg tama n Useqqif n Tmana (Micli). 

Cwit n lweqt, ifaq i tektiwen n ukabar n ugdud azzayri (PPA), dɣa yeɛed ad yesekcem timuzɣa deg ukabar aggi akw di tektiwin n ukabar aggi.  S waya ik yella gar wid i yeskren  ayen umi seman "la Crise berbériste" deg usegwas n 1949. Cwit n lweqt kkan, Aɛmar At Ḥemmuda yettfaṭef ger ifassen n Franca, anda yekcem ɣer lḥebs di Blida.

Asmi yella deg lḥebs di [[Blida]], akabar n Ugdud Aɣerfan n Lzzayer (PPA), yessufɣit di lufaq. 

Deg usegwas n 1950, [[Fransa]] tsereḥas, yeffeɣ-ed si lḥebs. Asmi id yefaɣ si lḥebs, yuɣal ixeddem di Lzzayer ar tama n [[Mbarek n At Mangellat]] akw d [[Baccir Bumaɛza]]. 

Asmi i yekker trad n 1954, yettwateḥem am "wemdakul n tektiwin n [[Messali Ḥaǧ]]" (yuggin di lawan-nni traḍ d umenuy ɣef timunent n tmurt n Lzzayer s leslaḥ). 

Dɣa yettwanɣa deg usegwas n 1956 ɣer f ufus n kra n yemjuḥad (ALN) deg tama n [[At Waɛban]] ([[Aqbil]] ).


